    "It also assists in the decision-making process in cases involving complex oral medicine.",
    "The primary objective of this review was to provide a detailed, evidence-based evaluation of ChatGPT's potential as a resource for medical and dental research, with the goal of directing future investigations and informing clinical practice.",
    "Within the medical community, ChatGPT is gaining recognition for its influence on both the healthcare system and medical field.",
    "It provides support as a complementary resource for diagnosis and decision-making across a variety of medical disciplines (14).",
    "Although the accuracy of its outputs and the potential for reinforcing biased diagnoses have prompted discussions on the necessity of human oversight when using this technology, ChatGPT can also be utilized in assessing disease risks and outcomes, advancing drug development, enhancing biomedical research, and transforming healthcare practice in significant ways (15) (16) (17)."
